------------------------------------------------------------
  Notes for reviewers
------------------------------------------------------------

* Every line is tagged MODE=PREVIEW or MODE=LIVE. Grep one or the
  other to filter the audit trail:
      Select-String -Path session-*.log -Pattern 'MODE=LIVE'
* User Ids referenced in PREVIEW entries start with "preview-"
  followed by a GUID -- those are the stub Ids Invoke-Action
  returns when -StubReturn was supplied. Real Ids appear only
  under MODE=LIVE.
* A live run uses the same Description strings under EXEC + OK or
  EXEC + ERROR entries -- this makes diffing a preview against a
  later live run trivial.
* Audit directory: %LOCALAPPDATA%\M365Manager\audit\ on Windows
  (inherits user-only NTFS ACLs from LOCALAPPDATA);
  ~/.m365manager/audit/ on POSIX, chmod 700 at first create.
